_header: My soul my Lord it magnifieth
_description: Audelay’s paraphrase of the Magnificat — eight 13-line stanzas

BodDou302.First Lines:
My soule my lord hit mangnefyþOure lady þus to here sun
                    con say…
BodDou302.Last Lines:
…With mangnifycat wen we ben hereAnima mea dominum
                    Explicit
